ent elections.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 304, \"end\": 310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6043188973450431, \"rank\": 0.6542099149533825, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 400, \"end\": 403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.9605638668193015e-18, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France President Emmanuel Macron has said he will not name a new government until after the 2024 Olympics in Paris, which start this week.\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999990814821684, \"rank\": 6.365615650095736e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 455, \"end\": 470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 547, \"end\": 552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999847309483, \"rank\": 1.5269263431767657e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"I confirm the full commitment of the French nation, and assure you that I will ask the next prime minister to include not only this guarantee but also an Olympic law in the priorities of the new government.\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 625, \"end\": 631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6043188973450431, \"rank\": 0.6542099149533825, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Seven years ago we made the same commitment (for Paris 2024), and we delivered.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5234903543199954e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will do the same.\\\"\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Under the French bid, the regions of Auvergne-Rhone-Alpes and Provence-Alpes-Cote d'Azur will host all major events at the 2030 Games.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6043188973450431, \"rank\": 0.6542099149533825, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 937, \"end\": 957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auvergne-Rh\\u00f4ne-Alpes\", \"score\": 0.9994302052304141, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Auvergne-Rhone-Alpes\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auvergne-Rh\\u00f4ne-Alpes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auvergne-Rh\\u00f4ne-Alpes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will be the fourth time that F